select memb.XObjectKey as ObjectKeyAssignedElement, elem.XObjectKey as ObjectKeyGroup, 'ApplicationGroup direct' as Reason, i.XObjectKey from ADSAccountInADSGroup i join ADSGroup elem on i.uid_ADSGroup = elem.uid_ADSGroup join ADSAccount memb on i.UID_ADSAccount = memb.UID_ADSAccount where elem.IsApplicationGroup = 1 and i.XOrigin & dbo.QBM_FGIBitPatternXOrigin ('|direct|', 0) > 0
union all
select memb.XObjectKey as ObjectKeyAssignedElement, elem.XObjectKey as ObjectKeyGroup, 'ApplicationGroup direct' as Reason, i.XObjectKey from ADSMachineInADSGroup i join ADSGroup elem on i.uid_ADSGroup = elem.uid_ADSGroup join ADSMachine memb on i.UID_ADSMachine = memb.UID_ADSMachine where elem.IsApplicationGroup = 1 and i.XOrigin & dbo.QBM_FGIBitPatternXOrigin ('|direct|', 0) > 0
-- LDAP-Anteil union all select memb.XObjectKey as ObjectKeyAssignedElement, elem.XObjectKey as ObjectKeyGroup, 'ApplicationGroup direct' as Reason, i.XObjectKey from LDPMachineInLDAPGroup i join LDAPGroup elem on i.uid_LDAPGroup = elem.uid_LDAPGroup join LDPMachine memb on i.uid_LDPMachine = memb.UID_LDPMachine where elem.IsApplicationGroup = 1 and i.XOrigin & dbo.QBM_FGIBitPatternXOrigin ('|direct|', 0) > 0
union all select memb.XObjectKey as ObjectKeyAssignedElement, elem.XObjectKey as ObjectKeyGroup, 'ApplicationGroup direct' as Reason, i.XObjectKey from LDAPAccountInLDAPGroup i join LDAPGroup elem on i.uid_LDAPGroup = elem.uid_LDAPGroup join LDAPAccount memb on i.uid_LDAPAccount = memb.UID_LDAPAccount where elem.IsApplicationGroup = 1 and i.XOrigin & dbo.QBM_FGIBitPatternXOrigin ('|direct|', 0) > 0
